    73	| `.opencode/skills/sk-doc/references/specific/manual_testing_playbook_creation.md` | Modified | §5: added "When to Use RCAF vs Natural-Human" subsection with rubric and voice guidelines |
    74	| `.opencode/commands/create/testing-playbook.md` | Modified | Line 317: clarified both prompt voices are valid |
    75	| `.opencode/skills/cli-claude-code/manual_testing_playbook/**` | Modified | Per-feature canonicals naturalized where appropriate |
